enumDescription: Possible error codes that could be returned by CheckoutUserError

values.name: BAD_DOMAIN
values.description: Input email contains an invalid domain name.

values.name: CART_DOES_NOT_MEET_DISCOUNT_REQUIREMENTS_NOTICE
values.description: Cart does not meet discount requirements notice.

values.name: CUSTOMER_ALREADY_USED_ONCE_PER_CUSTOMER_DISCOUNT_NOTICE
values.description: Customer already used once per customer discount notice.

values.name: GIFT_CARD_ALREADY_APPLIED
values.description: Gift card has already been applied.

values.name: GIFT_CARD_CURRENCY_MISMATCH
values.description: Gift card currency does not match checkout currency.

values.name: GIFT_CARD_DEPLETED
values.description: Gift card has no funds left.

values.name: GIFT_CARD_UNUSABLE
values.description: Gift card cannot be applied to a checkout that contains a gift card.

values.name: GREATER_THAN_OR_EQUAL_TO
values.description: The input value should be greater than or equal to the minimum value allowed.

values.name: INVALID_COUNTRY_AND_CURRENCY
values.description: Cannot specify country and presentment currency code.

values.name: INVALID_FOR_COUNTRY
values.description: Input Zip is invalid for country provided.

values.name: INVALID_FOR_COUNTRY_AND_PROVINCE
values.description: Input Zip is invalid for country and province provided.

values.name: LESS_THAN
values.description: The input value should be less than the maximum value allowed.

values.name: LESS_THAN_OR_EQUAL_TO
values.description: The input value should be less than or equal to the maximum value allowed.

values.name: LINE_ITEM_NOT_FOUND
values.description: Line item was not found in checkout.

values.name: PRESENT
values.description: The input value needs to be blank.

values.name: TOO_LONG
values.description: The input value is too long.

values.name: TOTAL_PRICE_MISMATCH
values.description: The amount of the payment does not match the value to be paid.
